---
title: Korean-Style Chicken Tacos with Pickled Onion, Crispy Shallots & Lime Aioli
description: A lip-smackingly good combo of garlic, soy and honey makes for some seriously tender and totally delicious
chicken. Give it the taco treatment by adding lime aioli, bright homemade pickled onion and fresh salad
ingredients, all wrapped up in soft flour tortillas for a Korean-style fiesta!

